assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: PT Waskita Karya (Persero) Tbk, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the engineering, procurement, and construction works in Indonesia. It constructs building projects, transportation facilities, and water resources and energy projects; invests in various toll roads; and operates realty projects. The company is also involved in the hotel management business; building and equipment rental business; and production of precast concrete. In addition, it operates as an independent power producer; and develops real estate properties. PT Waskita Karya (Persero) Tbk was founded in 1961 and is headquartered in Jakarta, Indonesia.
